{
  "stem": "3848.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But being that I showed them with epaulets, they thought that I was Polish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was part of a Polish stamp on the corner of the picture, because that picture was from one of my schools that I had on a certificate.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was written Polska, or Polish on there, so according to the picture, and looking at me, they decided yes, I am from Poland, and we send you back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is how I was able to get out of Russia in 1946, and I traveled to Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't easy, because they didn't give us any transportation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to hook on the road.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Being that I used to work on the railroad, I knew how to maneuver.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One train I traveled to Kiev from Poltava-- from Poltava to Kiev.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We saw a train that was going towards the city of Kiev, and it was coal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- a bunch of people from this Donskoe there-- we were together-- we climbed up on that-- on the top of the coal.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know the train goes, and the dust from the coal blows.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We came out all black.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we came to Kiev, we were like a chimney, just as black.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My uncle wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a different story about my uncle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Donskoe, in that same-- I have to go back to this place of Donskoe where he decided to volunteer to the Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he knew about his former wife and child, mother-in-law that was killed, because I told him that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Up to the time that I met him, he didn't know about his wife, his child-- I have a picture of them and his mother-in-law went to say goodbye to him in 1941 on the station.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The station was bombarded.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
